Jewellery ERP & Girvi Management Platform

Customer & KYC Module Specification v1.0

Module Code: MOD-CUSTOMER
Priority: Critical MVP
Version: 1.0
Frontend: Flutter + BLoC
Backend: NestJS
Dependencies: Authentication Module, Document Module, QR Module, Audit Module, Sync Module

⸻

1. Module Purpose

The Customer & KYC Module serves as the master customer registry for the entire platform.

Every Girvi, Savings Scheme, Retail Sale, Scrap Purchase, Compliance Form, and Audit Record must reference a valid customer profile.

The module is responsible for:

* Customer Creation
* Customer Search
* Aadhaar OCR
* PAN Management
* QR Customer Identification
* Customer Document Vault
* Customer Timeline
* Customer Risk Assessment
* Customer KYC Verification

