6. Business Rules

BR-CUST-001

Mobile number must be unique within tenant.

BR-CUST-002

Customer cannot be physically deleted.

BR-CUST-003

PAN mandatory if transaction exceeds ₹50,000.

BR-CUST-004

Aadhaar number must never be stored unmasked.

BR-CUST-005

Every customer receives Digital Customer ID.

BR-CUST-006

Every customer receives QR Code.

BR-CUST-007

All KYC documents encrypted at rest.

BR-CUST-008

Only Owner and Manager can view sensitive documents.

